ygData.msgSnippet: I found 8 ton warriors in about a week off and on, the 8th dropped it =)  Here is a hint: DON T hang out at the city! I found one out of the 8 there.  Instead,
ygData.messageBody:
I found 8 ton warriors in about a week off and on, the
8th dropped it =) Here is a hint: DON'T hang out at
the city! I found one out of the 8 there. Instead,
Head NE toward the little iksar mad guy camp, several
tons cross that area regularly. Also, in the general
north end of the map, with a tracker around you can
find many many more ton warriors then you ever did in
town.


--- Shawn Alley <shawna@...> wrote:
> congrats! I have the other 3 pieces (like many
> people I'm sure).
> Approximately how many ton warriors did you have to
> kill for the totem to
> drop? And did you find them only in the city in
> Swamp of no hope?
>
> Use caution when turning in your items. There is
> more than one kind of
> shaman powder. Probably if you use identify it will
> say "Nok Shaman
> Powder". I mention this as a friend has two "shaman
> powder" items, one
> black the other white. I have only black powder
> which came from a Nok
> Shaman so I believe black is the correct one.
>
> Azara Sparklemeister
> 20th Enchanter, Povar
>
> Shawn A.
